  ('Stage 17','boss','Control Fyro''s Turn Meter after the shield breaks — keep him in the vulnerable state as long as possible.','Decrease Turn Meter only','approved','human_observation','Sufficient at stages 15-17 where Fyro''s base speed is lower. At stages 18-20 the SPD floor increases — Decrease SPD may be needed to reliably prevent his turn.','fire-knight-ice-golem-seed-june-2026'),
  ('Stage 17','boss','Apply Decrease DEF and Weaken once shield is down to maximize damage in the window before it regenerates.','Decrease DEF + Weaken','approved','human_observation','Wired 2026-07-12: coverage goal had no solution (Fire Knight boss damage window).',null),
  ('Stage 17','boss','Break the shield every round before Fyro takes his turn — failure causes Max HP loss that compounds into a wipe.','Multi-Hit A1 champions + Increase Turn Meter','approved','human_observation','Increase Turn Meter grants the team extra turns = more attacks toward the shield each round. The FK guide lists a Speed champ with Increase Speed AND Increase Turn Meter as a core requirement. AND-combo: Turn Meter boost alone does not break a shield, so it pairs with multi-hit A1 champions.','fk-doc-gap-seed-2026-07-13'),
  ('Stage 17','boss','Break the shield every round before Fyro takes his turn — failure causes Max HP loss that compounds into a wipe.','Multi-Hit A1 champions + Ally Attack','approved','human_observation','Ally Attack forces all champions to strike simultaneously, generating many hits at once toward the shield. Fastest shield-break mechanism — especially valuable with at least one multi-hitter in the composition.','fire-knight-ice-golem-seed-june-2026'),
  ('Stage 17','boss','Break the shield every round before Fyro takes his turn — failure causes Max HP loss that compounds into a wipe.','Multi-Hit A1 champions + Counterattack buff','approved','human_observation','When Fyro attacks, Counterattack causes all buffed allies to retaliate immediately with their A1, generating additional hits. Works even if your base hit count is slightly below 10 per round.','fire-knight-ice-golem-seed-june-2026'),
  ('Stage 17','boss','Break the shield every round before Fyro takes his turn — failure causes Max HP loss that compounds into a wipe.','Multi-Hit A1 champions (5 × 2+ hits = 10+)','approved','human_observation','Five champions each hitting 2+ times per A1 generates 10+ hits per round — the minimum required at stages 10-20. Simplest solution that requires no special mechanics.','fire-knight-ice-golem-seed-june-2026'),
