  ('Stage 18','Spirit affinity stage (Magic has advantage). 10-hit shield. Fyro damage output increases at this tier — HP and DEF floors matter more.','AyumiLove Fire Knight guide + HellHades TM champions guide (2026)'),
  ('Stage 18','Almighty Immunity (passive): Fyro is immune to Stun, Freeze, Sleep, Provoke, Block Active Skills, Block Passive Skills, Fear and True Fear, plus HP-exchange, HP-balancing and cooldown-increase effects. Hard CC works only on the MINIONS, never on the boss — do not field a champion expecting to CC Fyro himself.','AyumiLove Fire Knight''s Castle guide (hand-read factual mechanics), 2026'),
  ('Stage 19','Magic affinity stage (Force has advantage). 10-hit shield. Dazzling Flames SPD debuff becomes more punishing here — team SPD buff uptime is critical.','AyumiLove Fire Knight guide + HellHades TM champions guide (2026)'),
  ('Stage 19','Almighty Immunity (passive): Fyro is immune to Stun, Freeze, Sleep, Provoke, Block Active Skills, Block Passive Skills, Fear and True Fear, plus HP-exchange, HP-balancing and cooldown-increase effects. Hard CC works only on the MINIONS, never on the boss — do not field a champion expecting to CC Fyro himself.','AyumiLove Fire Knight''s Castle guide (hand-read factual mechanics), 2026'),
  ('Stage 20','Force affinity stage (Magic has advantage). 10-hit shield. Stage 20 is the progression milestone for Arbiter missions and is confirmed as the sweet spot for energy efficiency. Additional passives unlock at stage 20 — verify exact passive from in-game Index before approving. Searing Storm destroys Max HP — repeated unbroken shields can compound into a wipe even for tanky teams.','AyumiLove Fire Knight guide + HellHades TM champions guide (2026)'),
  ('Stage 20','Almighty Immunity (passive): Fyro is immune to Stun, Freeze, Sleep, Provoke, Block Active Skills, Block Passive Skills, Fear and True Fear, plus HP-exchange, HP-balancing and cooldown-increase effects. Hard CC works only on the MINIONS, never on the boss — do not field a champion expecting to CC Fyro himself.','AyumiLove Fire Knight''s Castle guide (hand-read factual mechanics), 2026')
