  ('Stage 10','wave','Kill both minions before the boss phase — at stage 10-13 this is good practice but not yet survival-critical the way it is at stage 14+.','Block Revive','approved','human_observation','CORRECTED: requires ACC to land — not a guaranteed bypass. Still valuable at this stage range but will sometimes be resisted.','fire-knight-ice-golem-10-14-seed-june-2026'),
