  ('Stage 14','boss','At stage 14: treat Frigid Vengeance with the same caution as stage 15-20 — this is the confirmed transition stage where teams that ignored the mechanic at 10-13 start failing.','Block Revive + careful minion management','approved','human_observation','At stage 14, minion management becomes important — kill minions before HP thresholds hit, or use Block Revive (now correctly noted as ACC-dependent, not guaranteed).','fire-knight-ice-golem-10-14-seed-june-2026'),
  ('Stage 14','boss','At stage 14: treat Frigid Vengeance with the same caution as stage 15-20 — this is the confirmed transition stage where teams that ignored the mechanic at 10-13 start failing.','Poison stacking','approved','human_observation','At stage 14, switch to the same Poison/HP Burn approach used for stage 15-20 — bypasses Frigid Vengeance threshold triggers entirely.','fire-knight-ice-golem-10-14-seed-june-2026'),
  ('Stage 14','boss','Deal consistent damage to clear the boss — at stage 10-13, burst damage is survivable even if it triggers Frigid Vengeance, unlike stage 14+.','Direct AoE damage','approved','human_observation','At stage 10-13, straightforward burst damage clears the boss reliably. Frigid Vengeance triggers are survivable here even without careful management — multiple sources confirm players commonly just hit Klyssus at these stages and succeed.','fire-knight-ice-golem-10-14-seed-june-2026'),
  ('Stage 14','boss','Deal consistent damage to clear the boss — at stage 10-13, burst damage is survivable even if it triggers Frigid Vengeance, unlike stage 14+.','Poison stacking (forward-compatible approach)','approved','human_observation','Not required at stage 10-13 but establishes the habit/team composition that becomes necessary at stage 14+. Recommended if the player intends to push past stage 14 soon.','fire-knight-ice-golem-10-14-seed-june-2026'),
  ('Stage 15','wave','Kill both minions before the boss phase — alive minions during Frigid Vengeance make it team-wipe lethal.','Block Revive','approved','human_observation','Prevents minions from reviving when Frigid Vengeance triggers. Does not require ACC — bypasses the accuracy check entirely. Ensures clean boss phase even if minions were alive when threshold hit.','fire-knight-ice-golem-seed-june-2026'),
  ('Stage 15','wave','Kill both minions before the boss phase — alive minions during Frigid Vengeance make it team-wipe lethal.','AoE Damage + Decrease DEF','approved','human_observation','Kill both minions quickly with boosted AoE damage. Decrease DEF before hitting maximizes damage to ensure one-round or two-round kills.','fire-knight-ice-golem-seed-june-2026'),
  ('Stage 15','wave','Kill both minions before the boss phase — alive minions during Frigid Vengeance make it team-wipe lethal.','AoE Stun or Freeze','approved','human_observation','Denies minion turns while your team deals damage. Prevents dangerous minion skills from activating.','fire-knight-ice-golem-seed-june-2026'),
  ('Stage 15','boss','Avoid triggering Frigid Vengeance with burst damage — use Poison or HP Burn to gradually reduce boss HP through thresholds.','Block Revive + burst damage','approved','human_observation','Kill minions, apply Block Revive, then burst the boss through HP thresholds. Block Revive prevents minion revival so Frigid Vengeance triggers with no minions alive — only a weak DEF-ignore with low Freeze chance (20%). Requires very high damage output to execute before Numbing Chill disrupts the plan.','fire-knight-ice-golem-seed-june-2026'),
  ('Stage 15','boss','Avoid triggering Frigid Vengeance with burst damage — use Poison or HP Burn to gradually reduce boss HP through thresholds.','Poison stacking','approved','human_observation','Poison damage bypasses Frigid Vengeance HP threshold triggers entirely — the boss HP drops through thresholds from DoT ticks without triggering the counterattack. Most reliable approach at stages 15-20 Normal.','fire-knight-ice-golem-seed-june-2026'),
  ('Stage 15','boss','Avoid triggering Frigid Vengeance with burst damage — use Poison or HP Burn to gradually reduce boss HP through thresholds.','HP Burn','approved','human_observation','Same bypass mechanic as Poison — HP Burn ticks do not trigger Frigid Vengeance. Can be combined with Poison for faster clears.','fire-knight-ice-golem-seed-june-2026'),
  ('Stage 15','boss','Keep minions dead or Block Revive active — alive minions during Frigid Vengeance make it ignore 100% DEF and near-certain Freeze.','Block Revive','approved','human_observation','Prevents minion revival entirely — Frigid Vengeance still triggers but revives nothing, so DEF-ignore remains minimal (50% per alive minion = 0% with none alive).','fire-knight-ice-golem-seed-june-2026'),
