  ('Stage 14','boss','res','formula','200','Stage 14: RES 200+ recommended — same as stage 15+. Frigid Vengeance Freeze chance is the same mechanic as higher stages.'),
  ('Stage 14','boss','acc','formula','200','Stage 14 uses the SAME ACC floor as stage 15-20 — confirmed transition stage where Frigid Vengeance danger escalates sharply. Treat stage 14 with stage-15 rigor, not stage-10-13 rigor.'),
  ('Stage 14','boss','hp','formula','40000','Stage 14: HP 40000+ recommended — same floor as stage 15-20, not the relaxed stage 10-13 floor. This is the stage where teams that coasted through 10-13 start failing.'),
