  ('Stage 15','boss','res','formula','200','RES 200+ recommended to resist Frigid Vengeance Freeze at stages 15-20. Freeze chance is 20% base + 40% per alive minion — with 1 alive minion it''s 60%, with 2 alive it''s 100%. RES 200+ gives meaningful resistance against the 60% case. Against 100% Freeze (both minions alive), higher RES (300+) is needed. Treat as directional floor — primary source confirmation needed.'),
